text.section:
The Trust's report shall include:
The total amounts of funds expended;
The total amounts of funds committed;
The total amounts of funds remaining;
A list of projects for which funds have been expended or are committed;
A projection of projects in the near future for which grants will be made;
An assessment of which grants are expected to be fully or partially reimbursable to the Grant Fund;
An evaluation of the program's effectiveness; and
Projections as to future funding needs.
